msgid ""
"A lo largo del tiempo, gran parte de la riqueza musical lojana —incluyendo compositores,\n"
"                                intérpretes, obras y tradiciones— ha permanecido dispersa o en riesgo de perderse. Este proyecto busca \n"
"                                organizar esta información en un espacio accesible, moderno y dinámico."
msgstr ""
"Over time, much of Loja's musical wealth —including composers, performers, "
"works and traditions— has remained scattered or at risk of being lost. This "
"project seeks to organize this information in an accessible, modern and "
"dynamic space."

msgid "Guardar Cambios"
msgstr "Save Changes"

msgid ""
"Viaja a través de los siglos y descubre cómo Loja se convirtió en el "
"epicentro sonoro del Ecuador. Avanza por nuestra mágica calle musical."
msgstr ""
"Travel through the centuries and discover how Loja became the sonic "
"epicenter of Ecuador. Advance through our magical musical street."

msgid ""
"Cada artista en nuestra base de datos tiene una historia única que espera "
"ser descubierta por ti."
msgstr ""
"Each artist in our database has a unique story waiting to be discovered by "
"you."

msgid ""
"Rescate Digital es un proyecto vivo: seguimos digitalizando partituras y "
"biografías constantemente."
msgstr ""
"Digital Rescue is a living project: we continuously digitize sheet music and"
" biographies."

msgid "Cronología"
msgstr "Chronology"

msgid "Core Team"
msgstr "Core Team"

msgid ""
"Loja comienza a consolidarse como un centro cultural importante en el sur "
"del Ecuador."
msgstr ""
"Loja begins to consolidate as an important cultural center in southern "
"Ecuador."

msgid ""
"La creación de una página web dedicada al Rescate Digital de la Historia Musical Lojana\n"
"                                surge de la necesidad de preservar, difundir y revalorizar el patrimonio cultural de Loja, reconocido\n"
"                                como uno de los principales referentes musicales del Ecuador."
msgstr ""
"The creation of a website dedicated to the Digital Rescue of Loja's Musical "
"History arises from the need to preserve, disseminate and revalue the "
"cultural heritage of Loja, recognized as one of the main musical references "
"of Ecuador."

